operations of any Loan Party or any of its Subsidiaries or, to the best of the
Borrower's knowledge, tenants, which may give rise to any Environmental
Liabilities and Costs other than those in the aggregate that would have no
Material Adverse Effect. There are not now nor have there been in the past, any
events, conditions or circumstances with or arising from currently or previously
owned or leased properties or current or previous operations of any Loan Party
or any of its Subsidiaries or, to the best of the Borrower's knowledge, tenants,
